      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 01:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 起诉前员工涉嫌被盗文件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/meta-sues-disloyal-former-vp-over-alleged-stolen-documents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 起诉其一位前副总裁，称其叛逃到一家“秘密”人工智能云计算初创公司，称其为“令人震惊的”背叛行为。]]></description>
