      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:09:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rackspace Technology 即将与债权人达成重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/apollo-s-rackspace-nears-deal-for-debt-restructuring-new-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Rackspace Technology Inc. 即将与债权人达成重组协议，该协议将向其提供新现金、减少债务并重新调整债权人还款额度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/apollo-s-rackspace-nears-deal-for-debt-restructuring-new-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 22:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 称埃隆·马斯克在法庭文件中的说法“不连贯”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/openai-calls-musk-claims-incoherent-in-court-filing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 猛烈抨击埃隆·马斯克对其的指控，在一份法庭文件中表示，这位亿万富翁企业家的指控“基于令人费解的——”常常语无伦次——事实前提。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/openai-calls-musk-claims-incoherent-in-court-filing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 21:49:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CoinShares 称加密产品流入量飙升至历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/crypto-product-inflows-soar-to-record-high-coinshares-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 CoinShares International Ltd 称，今年投资者的兴趣浪潮正推动数十亿美元流入加密货币资产，将资金流入推至破纪录的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/crypto-product-inflows-soar-to-record-high-coinshares-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:45:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia ETF 实现双倍收益，流量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/nvidia-etf-that-delivers-double-gains-sees-record-flows-volume</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着交易量和资金流入创下历史新高，人工智能多头越来越倾向于一只 ETF，该 ETF 加大了对 Nvidia Corp. 的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/nvidia-etf-that-delivers-double-gains-sees-record-flows-volume</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型云合同刺激预订量增长后，甲骨文股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/oracle-sales-beat-estimates-as-cloud-growth-stabilizes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甲骨文公司股价飙升 13%，此前该公司报告称其备受关注的云计算业务导致预订量激增，显示其在争夺更多竞争市场份额方面取得了进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/oracle-sales-beat-estimates-as-cloud-growth-stabilizes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 20:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Advent International 正在考虑以 10 亿美元出售 CAES</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/advent-international-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-sale-of-caes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Advent International 正在考虑出售 CAES，这可能会使这家航空航天和国防技术公司的估值超过 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/advent-international-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-sale-of-caes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 19:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reddit 的 IPO、比特币的崛起和 SVB 的崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-11/reddit-s-ipo-bitcoin-s-rise-and-svb-s-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的卡罗琳·海德 (Caroline Hyde) 和埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 详细介绍了 Reddit IPO 的最新细节，这家社交媒体公司希望筹集近 7.5 亿美元资金，而比特币价格首次突破 72,000 美元。此外，维诺德·科斯拉 (Vinod Khosla) 讨论了自一年前硅谷银行倒闭以来风险投资生态系统的状况，并分享了他对埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 OpenAI 诉讼的看法。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-11/reddit-s-ipo-bitcoin-s-rise-and-svb-s-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 19:19:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Reddit 启动期待已久的 IPO，目标募集资金 7.48 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/reddit-launches-long-awaited-ipo-with-748-million-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Reddit Inc. 披露了今年最大的首次公开募股之一的更多细节，该公司和一些现有股东寻求筹集高达 7.48 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/reddit-launches-long-awaited-ipo-with-748-million-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 10:23:10 GMT</pubDate>
